{
  "stem": "15962.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But later on that year, there was-- here and there, there were kind of remarks dropped inadvertently, I suppose, or out of-- not necessarily out of spite-- by kids, you know, that I'm a dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that happened very seldom, at least at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I was never told to, to conceal it, although I, I, I think the only way that children would know that was because of that religious one hour of week when I was n-- with neither the Catholics nor the Protestants.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we moved into a beautiful villa of some very wealthy relatives where we have everything that we wanted.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were even picked up by, by their limousine and their chauffeurs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we didn't, we didn't seem to be at all deprived of anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were no shortages at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, because there were, there were people-- and the men were called in to the armed forces.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was certainly a very tense time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, three or four months-- and then when the Munich conference took place and the so-called Allies gave part of Czechoslovakia to Hitler, that was the end of that crisis.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a tremendous let down for the nation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went back home-- not for long, because six months later, Hitler marched into the rest of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And since we were on the border, we were one of the first to see the troops move in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I recall waking up early one morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was still almost dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my parents were glued to what was a radio receiver, which was a very primitive kind of crystal set.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one could hardly hear what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
